        "## Predicting Key 2023 Development Outcomes from 2014 Data - Our Robustness check üëÄ\n",
        "\n",
        "To demonstrate that our multivariate **Development Index**‚Äîderived via PCA on seven thematic pillars‚Äîcaptures deeper aspects of a country‚Äôs trajectory than income alone, we ran a series of pairwise regressions predicting ten flagship indicators in 2023.  In each case, we compare:\n",
